About Lake Deaton RV Park
We offer short and long term rentals of our 82 full hookup lots
Our park, situated on Lake Deaton, in Wildwood, FL, is surrounded by natural beauty and provides the convenience of being close to both the east and west coasts, as well as the Orlando and Tampa area attractions.

Come experience the charm and beauty of our 82 site adult park.Â Our private dock offers a place for the fisherman to cast a line, or a place to sit back and relax. Bring your canoe, kayak or boat, and enjoy all Lake Deaton has to offer.
Our proximity to The Villages Town Squares of Lake Sumter Landing, Spanish Springs and Brownwood, offers dining, shopping and entertainment. Our area also offers fishing, biking, and walking trails as well as access to the many golf courses in the area.
